    "Title": "Eliminate XenoThreat Idris",
    "Description": "Hey, \n\nThe rumors are true. XenoThreat has deployed an Idris to stalk and attack Citizens for Prosperity operations in a dramatic escalation of their hostility towards us. We just received word the ship, under the command of ~mission(TargetName), is advancing toward ~mission(location|address). We can\u2019t get our own forces there fast enough to fight them, and are in desperate need of help. \n\nWe\u2019re looking to hire someone brave enough to take it to these bastards. It\u2019s not enough to scare them away, we need to guarantee that it can\u2019t come after us again. \n\nNot sure if you\u2019ve faced down an Idris before, but it\u2019s a tall task for someone to take on alone. I\u2019d highly recommend recruiting others to the cause.   \n\nBest,\n\nLima Endicott\nLead Dispatcher\nCitizens for Prosperity",
